history.”

11
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:35,950
Well, not what I was thinking either.

12
00:00:35,950 --> 00:00:41,559
Yes, China is killing millions of innocent
meditators for their organs.

13
00:00:41,559 --> 00:00:45,530
Which is what a lot of people might call “genocide.”

14
00:00:45,530 --> 00:00:49,940
This comes after this incredibly detailed
680-page report

15
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:54,690
revealed that as many as 1.5 million innocent
people in China

16
00:00:54,690 --> 00:00:57,309
have been murdered for their organs.

17
00:00:57,309 --> 00:00:59,530
And I’m not talking about this being done
by some

18
00:00:59,530 --> 00:01:01,920
underground gangs or criminal networks.

19
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:05,400
I’m talking about official hospitals.

20
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:08,720
Including hospitals run by the Chinese military.

21
00:01:08,720 --> 00:01:12,080
Like this one, the 301 Military Hospital in
Beijing.

22
00:01:12,080 --> 00:01:17,780
It’s a place where a lot of high-ranking
Community Party members get treated.

23
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:21,479
The Chinese military is killing Chinese citizens
for their organs

24
00:01:21,479 --> 00:01:23,890
on a massive scale.

25
00:01:23,890 --> 00:01:27,829
And across China, other hospitals have been
following their example.

26
00:01:27,829 --> 00:01:36,680
“The Chinese regime not only deprives its
people of their basic rights on a daily basis,

27
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:40,590
but literally steals their body parts for
a profit.”

28
00:01:40,590 --> 00:01:44,990
Because there’s nothing more valuable than
a human life.

29
00:01:44,990 --> 00:01:50,189
Now you’d think that this discovery should
be making major international headlines.

30
00:01:50,189 --> 00:01:54,049
And to a degree, that’s happened.

31
00:01:54,049 --> 00:01:58,810
The problem is that news, like comedy, is
all about…

32
00:01:58,810 --> 00:02:00,060
…timing!

33
00:02:00,060 --> 00:02:02,820
And the timing for this wasn't the greatest.

34
00:02:02,820 --> 00:02:05,070
Hashtag Brexit.

35
00:02:05,070 --> 00:02:07,590
But this story is still huge.

36
00:02:07,590 --> 00:02:10,830
And the long-term implications haven’t even
begun to set in.

37
00:02:10,830 --> 00:02:16,480
Eventually, I think it’s going mean more
countries will go from attitudes like this:

38
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:20,520
“I think this is going to be a very important
moment for British-Chinese relations

39
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,560
which are in a very good state,

40
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:25,440
something of a golden era in our relationship.”

41
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:27,080
...to attitudes like this:

42
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:35,120
“We recommend an international investigation
into forced organ harvesting in China,

43
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:39,160
and that the British government take a lead.”

44
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:41,720
Because it’s hard to have a golden era with
a regime

45
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:44,260
that’s currently committing crimes against
humanity.

46
00:02:44,260 --> 00:02:47,250
I mean, once enough people know about it.

47
00:02:47,250 --> 00:02:50,700
So, here’s what people ought to know about
it.

48
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:51,810
In most of the world,

49
00:02:51,810 --> 00:02:55,870
it takes months or years to get an organ transplant.

50
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:58,420
But in China, it’s so easy!

51
00:02:58,420 --> 00:03:03,210
“Patients typically must wait only a few
weeks for a donor organ.”

52
00:03:03,210 --> 00:03:07,940
And they somehow perform a crazy number of
organ transplants there.

53
00:03:07,940 --> 00:03:13,090
Officials say there's a total of 10,000 organ
transplants a year in China.

54
00:03:13,090 --> 00:03:15,190
But this report finds that there are,

55
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:18,800
in fact, mega hospitals across the country,

56
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:21,420
each with thousands of beds,

57
00:03:21,420 --> 00:03:24,320
performing thousands of transplants.

58
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:26,330
So many, that, according to the report,

59
00:03:26,330 --> 00:03:27,410
many surgeons have simply

60
00:03:27,410 --> 00:03:31,040
“lost count” of how many they performed.

61
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:33,180
Using data gathered from Chinese media reports

62
00:03:33,180 --> 00:03:35,760
and the websites of individual hospitals,

63
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:38,130
the report goes on to estimate that between

64
00:03:38,130 --> 00:03:41,980
60,000 to 100,000 political prisoners are
killed

65
00:03:41,980 --> 00:03:43,850
—every year—

66
00:03:43,850 --> 00:03:46,870
to supply China’s hospitals with fresh organs.

67
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:50,290
By contrast, the total number of transplants
in the US

68
00:03:50,290 --> 00:03:53,770
in most years is less than 30,000.

69
00:03:53,770 --> 00:03:56,190
Of course this raises the question:

70
00:03:56,190 --> 00:04:00,100
If the Chinese Communist Party is killing
all these people for their organs,

71
00:04:00,100 --> 00:04:02,080
where are these people coming from?

72
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:06,610
Wouldn’t, you know, people in China start
to question so many disappearances?

73
00:04:06,610 --> 00:04:09,320
Well, not if the Party convinces you

74
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:11,290
that a certain group of people,

75
00:04:11,290 --> 00:04:15,880
aren’t really people, and can be treated
however they want.

76
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:18,590
Is there...any group like that in China?

77
00:04:18,590 --> 00:04:20,410
Falun Gong practitioners.

78
00:04:20,410 --> 00:04:22,410
The people who are thrown into labor camps

79
00:04:22,410 --> 00:04:24,770
for doing this.

80
00:04:24,900 --> 00:04:29,200
That’s where the vast majority of the organs
are coming from, according to Bloody Harvest.

81
00:04:29,210 --> 00:04:33,310
The report also says that other organ "donors"

82
00:04:33,310 --> 00:04:36,200
include Tibetans, Uyghurs, and House Christians.

83
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:39,510
Note that one of the report’s authors is
David Kilgour,

84
00:04:39,510 --> 00:04:44,100
who’s Canada’s former Secretary of State
for Asia-Pacific.

85
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:48,110
Bloody Harvest goes into detail about the
evidence behind their claim

86
00:04:48,110 --> 00:04:53,070
that Falun Gong practitioners make up the
majority of organ harvesting victims.

87
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:57,470
Like how undercover investigators called dozens
of Chinese hospitals,

88
00:04:57,470 --> 00:05:00,310
asking for those healthy Falun Gong organs.

89
00:05:00,310 --> 00:05:03,160
