Investigator:\h\h\h I just want to know how
long we have to wait.

94
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:12,000
Doctor Dai:\h\h\h We have supplies everyday.

95
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:12,880
Today for example,

96
