97
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:18,140
Investigator:\h\h\h Well, I mean not just
a fresh one.

98
00:05:18,260 --> 00:05:19,880
We need one from live human body…

99
00:05:20,060 --> 00:05:21,480
Doctor Dai:\h\h\h Sure, the organs we use
are all from live persons.

100
00:05:21,580 --> 00:05:22,080
Investigator:\h\h\h What?

101
00:05:22,340 --> 00:05:23,880
Doctor Dai:\h\h\h They are all live organs!

102
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:25,540
Ours are the best.

103
