107
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,820
Doctor Dai:\h\h\h We’ve done this for 5-6
years.

108
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:36,780
We have performed such kind of operation for
5-6 years already.

109
00:05:36,900 --> 00:05:38,860
Investigator:\h\h\h Then how many do you do
per month?

110
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:40,180
Doctor Dai:\h\h\h We have done 400 to 500
cases.

111
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:42,320
