read the 680-page report,

120
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:12,480
the last 230 pages of which are filled with
all of their references,

121
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:16,480
because man, there’s a lot of facts.

122
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:18,810
But China’s Foreign Ministry had a better
solution

123
00:06:18,810 --> 00:06:21,120
than reading the report and addressing the
facts.

124
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:24,480
It simply removed the reporter's question 
and her answer

125
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:27,200
from that day's official press conference transcript.

126
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:30,040
Now no one will know!

127
