China.

145
00:07:23,210 --> 00:07:26,330
Because now that this news is getting more
and more attention,

146
00:07:26,330 --> 00:07:28,710
Chinese authorities will have to do more to
address it

147
00:07:28,710 --> 00:07:33,200
than simply deleting all mentions of it from
the Foreign Ministry website.

148
